raw_data.notes: Only symptomatic patient from Rajpura passed away on 27th April at Rajindra Hospital, Patiala.
Covid-19 test confirmation came on Apr 21. He was suffering from severe liver disease and breathlessness when he was admitted to GIMS. He passed away on Apr 27th.
These deaths are from 20th April to April 25th as per the state bulletin but announced on Apr 27th.
